Beautiful and meticulously maintained town home with open and spacious design,  
walking distance from the Albertville Outlet Mall!

Main Level
Foyer
Light and spacious area to welcome your guests. 
Living Room
This great space has natural lighting and a beautiful view of the lake across the street!  The 9 foot high ceilings makes this home feel warm and elegant.  The living room hosts neutral décor.  
Informal Dining Room
A great space positioned next to the kitchen and open to the living room provides open concept living.  This is a great floor plan for entertaining guests!
Kitchen
Chef?s kitchen with an abundance of maple cabinetry.  Gleaming granite counter tops with a breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances and recessed lighting makes this kitchen very desirable.
Upper Level
Family Room
Located at the top of the stairs is a spacious family room with plenty of room for family gatherings, games or movies!  A comfortable place to relax at the end of the day!
Master Bedroom
This Master suite has a very elegant feel with lake views.   Big windows offer plenty of natural light. There is a spacious walk-in closet for all your wardrobe needs.  The master bath is a walk thru with double sinks, plenty of counter space, a full tub and maple cabinetry.

Second Bedroom
A nice sized room with abundant closet space, and neutral decor.  
Laundry 
Washer and Dryer included in Sale. Located on the upper level it is conveniently close to the bedrooms!

Additional Features

Pets Allowed

description:
Recently sold: $304,000. MAIN LEVEL 

Living Room
The living room is large and bright with an abundance of natural light shining in. It has recessed lighting, plenty of space for entertaining, a gas fireplace, and is open to the dining room. The foyer is also adjacent to the living room and contains a closet.

Kitchen 
The kitchen showcases an ample amount of built-in hardwood cabinetry, hardwood floors, a large pantry, plenty of counter space, stainless steel appliances, and is open to the informal dining room.

Informal Dining
The informal dining room is open to both the kitchen and living room. It has hardwood floors, windows allowing plenty of light. Sliding glass doors lead you to the private patio and large backyard. 

Main Floor Laundry
The laundry room is conveniently located on the main floor. It has plenty of storage space, washer & dryer, laundry sink, and is connected to the garage so it can double as a mud room.

Bedroom 1
The bedroom on the main level is carpeted, has a window for natural lighting and a closet. Conveniently located near the ¾ bathroom.

UPPER LEVEL

Master Bedroom
The master bedroom is generous in size with a ceiling fan, two large windows, carpet, a private ¾ bath with double sinks, and a walk-in closet!

Bedroom 3 
Adjacent to the master bedroom is another great sized room with a private full bathroom and large walk in closet. This room has tons of natural light, built in window seat, and a ceiling fan. 

LOWER LEVEL
Family Room 
This family room is massive with 8ft ceilings, plush carpet, and recessed lighting throughout. The egress window in this family room sends through an abundance of natural light. An additional electric heat source is available with a separate thermostat.

Bedroom 4 
This bedroom is bright and carpeted. Conveniently located near a ¾ bathroom with heated tile floors.
Storage/Mechanical
This clean storage room is great for all your storage needs.

Special Features
-	Backyard Overlooks Neighborhood Parks
-	Popular and Welcoming Neighborhood
-	Large 3 Car Garage 35 x 25
-	Gas & Electric Line Installed
-	Luxurious Insulated Garage Doors 2015
-	35 x 19 Patio
-	29 x 08 Front Porch
-	Very Well Maintained ? One Owner Home
-	Professionally Landscaped
-	New Roof in 2008
-	In ground Sprinkler System
-	STMA Award Winning School District
